======
RULES
======

[ > player | crate ] -> [ > player | > crate ]
[ > crate | crate ] -> [ > crate | > crate ]

[ > crate | tail no tailend ] -> cancel
[ > player | body no tailend ] -> cancel
[ > player | wall ] -> cancel
[ > crate | wall ] -> cancel

[ > head | ... | no crate | ...| tail tailend ] -> [ > head noeat_token | ... | | ... | tail tailend ]

up [ > head no noeat_token | > crate | ...  | tail tailend ] -> [ tail c_up | c_down head digestion | ...  | tail tailend ]
down [ > head no noeat_token | > crate| ...  | tail tailend ] -> [ tail c_down | c_up head digestion | ...  | tail tailend ]
left [ > head no noeat_token | > crate | ... | tail tailend ] -> [ tail c_left | c_right head digestion | ...  | tail tailend ]
right [ > head no noeat_token | > crate | ...  | tail tailend ] -> [ tail c_right | c_left head digestion | ...  | tail tailend ]

[ noeat_token ] -> [ ]

(let player move into own tail somehow lol)
[> head | tail no tailend] -> cancel
(you can't move into your tail while growing)

[ > player | > crate | no body no crate ] -> [ > player |  | crate ]

[ > crate  | no body no crate ] -> [  | crate ]
[ > player | > crate | body ] -> [ > player |  | body ]

(snakey movement!)

( [ tailend ] -> [ tailend propagation_token ]  )

(delete the tail end piece, and the connector to it)

random up [moving player] [ tail tailend c_up | c_down ] -> [moving player] [ | tailend ]
+ down [moving player] [ tail tailend c_down | c_up ] -> [moving player] [ | tailend ]
+ left [moving player] [ tail tailend c_left | c_right ] -> [moving player] [ | tailend ]
+ right [moving player] [ tail tailend c_right | c_left ] -> [moving player] [ | tailend ]

up [ > player | ] -> [ tail c_up | c_down player ]
down [ > player | ] -> [ tail c_down | c_up player ]
left [ > player | ] -> [ tail c_left | c_right player ]
right [ > player | ] -> [ tail c_right | c_left player ]

late [ digestion no body ] -> [ wall ]

